      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">True No-Vowel Words — The Welsh Trio</h2>

      <p>Only three words in the entire Scrabble dictionary contain no A, E, I, O, U, or Y. All three come from Welsh, where W functions as a vowel.</p>

